🚨 BREAKING BANT: NIGERIAN EXAMS BE LIKE… 😂🚨

You go read textbook from page 1 to 200, cram all the formulas, memorize definitions, even do midnight prayers. Na so you reach exam hall, open question paper and see:
"If Sapa is directly proportional to your account balance, explain why salary no dey last 2 days." 😭

Omo, who send me read textbook?! 😂😂
Have you ever seen a question that made you rethink your life? Drop your experience! 👇🏽😅

